&+WFrobbing Policy
&+b---------------
Frobs can be given by ArchWizards and above to players if they have proved to 
be a Wizard+ on any MUD in the AberMUD family. Note that the frob will be
added onto your current score.

Ranking on other MUDs     Points To Frob         Level (From Level 0)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Wizard                            50,000                           8
Power (Arch-Wiz and Above)        70,000                           9
Master User (MUD Owner, God)      90,000                           9
----------------------------------------------------------------------

